Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧  少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  中校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS的…性能测试…
