Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了啦  被你拉着到处转
