Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学得不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:07.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  沙慈  快来看看
