Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  阿雷路亚·哈普提兹姆他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个重力块完全脱离了空间站
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说在漂流中？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援队马上就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持到那时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有7分钟就要到达临界脱离区域了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让重力块回到原本的高度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有让那个庞然大物加速才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:44.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才计算了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个重力区域还有5分钟就要落入地球引力圈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙…沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑吧  只剩下5分钟…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.55,0:16:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第7区域的质量太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠这台机体的推进力…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离到达临界脱离区域还有200秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去我的机体也要被吸入重力圈里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能对这200多人见死不救吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙啊  你为什么如此无情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个以高速接近的机体是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么到现在雷达才发现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:40.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Gundam吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷路亚  阿雷路亚·哈普提兹姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你的任务呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是无法明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.06,0:16:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙漂流者的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离到达临界脱离区域还有20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:16:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又  又有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  Celestial Being竟然会救人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就看皇小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美发出了紧急机密讯号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救人…  那个孩子在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:47.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速报  空间站事故的失踪者名单出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使有Gundam那样的推进力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持现状也已经是极限了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  燃料用尽以后  也只能落入地球圈了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听得到吗  全员集中到中央区域
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音  是Gundam的机师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍  不想死的话  赶快集中到中央去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…援救行动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻男子的声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定这次就没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想现在就对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.13,0:18:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听到吗  Gundam机师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个东西马上就要进入脱离极限的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了  赶快放开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being是不允许失败的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.75,0:19:02.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.01,0:19:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对沙慈你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Meister可不是一个人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·斯托拉托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子高浓度压缩中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距填充完毕还有20  19  18  17  16…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射方向的轴线上有云挡着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它切开  刹那！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填充完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒的支援  皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从地面狙击那两个重力块让它们分离开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,减轻重量后  再把它推入安全轨道…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援队来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中…中校  Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援行动是最优先的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是我  也是知道感恩的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速报  全员安全获救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.38,0:21:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吠陀安排的任务  优先去救人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  Dynames的高精度狙击能力也向全世界暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要大幅度修正本来的计划呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变原来的任务  向洛克昂·斯托拉托斯下达命令的可是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.91,0:21:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是为了帮助阿雷路亚·哈普提兹姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.64,0:21:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为了保护Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是只要适性相符合  就都能乘上Gundam的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们差点就死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.91,0:21:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最后想说的…到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.58,0:22:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.21,0:23:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使在一成不变的战场上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.09,0:23:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being也不会保持沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.04,0:23:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配置了新武器的Gundam们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.08,0:23:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要向世界表明自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「七剑」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经再也回不来了
